description:
Supplementary data for "Identification of Obelisk-like RNA replicons in hot springs and expansion of the diversity of the Obelisk superfamily" 
 &nbsp; 
 A preprint can be found at bioRxiv:&nbsp;doi: https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.09.03.673927 
 &nbsp; 
 This version refers to data after revision. 
 v.2.1 contains summary files of the data used to generate individual graphs (Source_data_fig.zip) 
 &nbsp; 
 First version (HSObl 1.0.0) was entitled: Data for "Double-stranded RNA sequencing identifies Obelisk-like covalently closed circular (ccc) RNA replicon in hot springs and extends diversity of the Obelisk superfamily"

